{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "pharmaflow-security-v2",
		"name": "User Health Service API - Security Documented",
		"description": "Complete API collection with JWT Authentication & Authorization examples.\n\n**Security Implementation:**\n- JWT-based authentication\n- Role-based access control (RBAC)\n- Token blacklist for logout\n- 401 Unauthorized for invalid/missing tokens\n- 403 Forbidden for insufficient permissions\n\n**Roles:**\n- ROLE_USER: Basic user, can view own data\n- ROLE_DOCTOR: Can manage patient health profiles\n- ROLE_PHARMACIST: Can access inventory\n- ROLE_ADMIN: Full access to all endpoints",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "baseUrl",
			"value": "http://localhost:8081",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "accessToken",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "refreshToken",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "1. Authentication",
			"description": "Authentication endpoints - login, register, refresh, logout",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Register New User (ROLE_USER)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', jsonData.accessToken);",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', jsonData.refreshToken);",
									"    console.log('✅ Tokens saved. Access token expires in: ' + jsonData.expiresIn + 'ms');",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"firstName\": \"John\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Doe\",\n  \"email\": \"john.doe@pharmaflow.ba\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123!\",\n  \"role\": \"ROLE_USER\"\n}",
							"options": {
								"raw": {
									"language": "json"
								}
							}
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
						}
					},
					"response": []
				},
